tag: WIFI, flight
status: done
summary:
two approach:
  1. Air to ground (ATG) system
    https://concourse.gogoair.com/gogo-atg-4-work/
    lower frequency (800 MHz),limited to 10 Mbps, low latency
  2. Satellite system
    satellite internet are Ku-band (12–18 GHz) and Ka-band (26–40 GHz)
    bandwidth between 30 to 100 Mbps per aircraft
    expensive
    high latency
    https://concourse.gogoair.com/infographic-far-gogo-2ku-data-travel/
    
